---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ NAV ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#F7F5F2]/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-[#D6D2CC]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] tracking-tight shrink-0">Scott McFall</span>
      <nav class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="#services" class="nav-link text-sm text-[#6B7280] hover:text-[#1C1C1C] transition-colors">Services</a>
        <a href="#work" class="nav-link text-sm text-[#6B7280] hover:text-[#1C1C1C] transition-colors">Work</a>
        <a href="#process" class="nav-link text-sm text-[#6B7280] hover:text-[#1C1C1C] transition-colors">Process</a>
      </nav>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="text-sm font-semibold bg-[#D97706] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-[#B45309] hover:scale-[1.03] active:scale-[0.97] transition-all shrink-0"
      >
        Let's Work Together
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ HERO ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-16">
      <p class="fade-up text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-4" style="animation-delay: 0ms">AI Developer</p>
      <h1 class="fade-up text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1C1C1C] mb-6" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
        I build AI-powered tools and workflows for creators and founders.
      </h1>
      <p class="fade-up text-lg text-[#6B7280] mb-8 max-w-xl" style="animation-delay: 160ms">
        From custom calculators to real-time web apps to post-production automation. I ship things that actually work, and I use AI to do it faster than most.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="fade-up inline-block bg-[#D97706] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-[#B45309] hover:scale-[1.03] active:scale-[0.97] transition-all"
        style="animation-delay: 240ms"
      >
        Let's Work Together ‚Üí
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ CREDIBILITY ROW ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section class="border-t border-b border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#EDEAE6]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] text-center">
          Projects shipped for <span class="text-[#1C1C1C] font-medium">Lewis Howes & School of Greatness</span>,
          <span class="text-[#1C1C1C] font-medium">JJ Virgin</span>,
          indie founders, schools, and content creators.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ SERVICES ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="services" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">What I Build</h2>
      <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">I keep my focus narrow so I can do each thing well.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üöÄ</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Landing Pages & Lead Capture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Fast pages that look good and actually load. Forms, CTAs, and tracking included.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Custom Tools & Calculators</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Lead magnets, configurators, calculators. Interactive tools your audience uses, not just visits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 160ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Workflow Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Cut the repetitive stuff. File processing, data pipelines, internal tools built to save real hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ CASE STUDIES ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="work" class="bg-[#EDEAE6] border-t border-[#D6D2CC]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Work</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">Real projects, real outcomes.</p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Project 1 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Health & Nutrition</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">Protein Calculator ‚Äî JJ Virgin</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Built for bestselling author & health expert JJ Virgin</li>
              <li>‚Üí Personalized daily protein targets based on user inputs</li>
              <li>‚Üí Embedded as a lead capture tool on her site</li>
              <li>‚Üí Helps grow her email list on autopilot</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 2 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Real-Time Web App</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">Live Auction Site ‚Äî School Fundraiser</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Real-time bid updates without page refresh</li>
              <li>‚Üí Replaced a spreadsheet and clipboard process entirely</li>
              <li>‚Üí Handled concurrent bidders smoothly on event night</li>
              <li>‚Üí Shipped in days, not weeks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 3 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Workflow Automation</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">MP3 ID3 Tag Batch Processor</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Automates writing ID3 metadata tags across large audio libraries</li>
              <li>‚Üí Eliminated hours of manual file editing per batch</li>
              <li>‚Üí Custom rules engine for consistent tagging standards</li>
              <li>‚Üí Built for producers managing large back-catalog audio libraries</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 4 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Custom Interface</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">YouTube Competitor Interface</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Custom video browsing UI built on top of YouTube's API</li>
              <li>‚Üí Tailored UX for a specific content niche and audience</li>
              <li>‚Üí Strips out ads, recommendations, and noise</li>
              <li>‚Üí Shows what you can build when you're not limited by a platform</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 5 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 sm:col-span-2 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 40ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Podcast Post-Production</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">AI Workflow Automation ‚Äî Lewis Howes / School of Greatness</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2 sm:columns-2">
              <li>‚Üí Built AI-assisted tools to automate parts of the post-production process for School of Greatness</li>
              <li>‚Üí Cut out manual steps between recording and publish-ready files</li>
              <li>‚Üí Faster episode turnaround without adding headcount</li>
              <li>‚Üí Designed to keep up with a consistent weekly publishing schedule</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ PROCESS ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="process" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">How I Work</h2>
      <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">Simple, fast, and collaborative.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Discover</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">We talk through your goal, your audience, and what success actually looks like. Better to ask the hard questions up front.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Build</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">I build fast using AI-assisted development. You see working software early, not mockups or decks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Launch</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">We ship, test, and adjust. You end up with something live that you own and can maintain, not a black box.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ CONTACT ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="contact" class="bg-[#EDEAE6] border-t border-[#D6D2CC]">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Let's Work Together</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-8">Tell me what you're building. I'll tell you if and how I can help.</p>

        <!-- Replace YOUR_FORMSPREE_ID with your actual ID from https://formspree.io -->
        <form
          action="https://formspree.io/f/xwvnnpoy"
          method="POST"
          class="space-y-5"
        >
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] mb-1">Your name</label>
              <input
                id="name"
                type="text"
                name="name"
                required
                placeholder="Jane Smith"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#F7F5F2] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-[#1C1C1C] placeholder-[#9CA3AF] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706]"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] mb-1">Email address</label>
              <input
                id="email"
                type="email"
                name="email"
                required
                placeholder="jane@example.com"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#F7F5F2] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-[#1C1C1C] placeholder-[#9CA3AF] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706]"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="project" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] mb-1">Tell me about your project</label>
            <textarea
              id="project"
              name="project"
              rows="5"
              required
              placeholder="What are you trying to build? What's the goal? What's the timeline?"
              class="w-full rounded-md border border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#F7F5F2] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-[#1C1C1C] placeholder-[#9CA3AF] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706] resize-none"
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-[#D97706] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-[#B45309] transition-colors"
          >
            Send Message ‚Üí
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div class="mt-14 space-y-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg">Quick answers</h3>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] text-sm">What kinds of projects are a good fit?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] mt-1">Custom tools, calculators, landing pages, and small-to-mid web apps. If you have a clear problem and a real audience, reach out.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] text-sm">How fast do you typically ship?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] mt-1">Most projects have something working within a week. Full launches are usually 2 to 4 weeks depending on scope.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] text-sm">Do you work with non-technical clients?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] mt-1">Yes, and most of my clients are. You know your audience and your problem. I handle the technical side.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] text-sm">What does "AI-assisted" mean in practice?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] mt-1">It means I use AI tools throughout the build process to move faster. Same quality, more output, shorter timelines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ FOOTER ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
  <footer class="border-t border-[#D6D2CC]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">¬© 2026 Scott McFall. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/scottmcfalldev-bot"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] hover:text-[#1C1C1C] transition-colors"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
